The evidence with the title 'Up in the air (2009 film) - Wikipedia ' says Up in the Air is a 2009 American comedy-drama film directed by Jason Reitman and written by Reitman and Sheldon Turner , based on the 2001 novel of the same name , written by Walter Kirn. The story is centered on corporate "downsizer " Ryan Bingham (George Clooney) and his travels.  ... The Los Angeles premiere was at the Mann Village Theater on november 30  ... 
